author: julianfoad
msg: Add a local function fetch_repos_id() which is the same as create_repos_id()
except it doesn't create an id if not found; instead it returns an error.
This makes the calling code easier to reason about, and paves the way for
removing this look-up entirely in callers where the repos-id was retrieved
earlier but was converted to a URL and UUID pair.
